%3BBy%20collaborating%20on%20transformational%2C%20world-class%20research%20programs%20harnessing%20new%20technology%20and%20compute%20capability%20we%20will%20together%20deliver%20positive%20impact%20on%20society%20at%20scale.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oracle%20cofounder%2C%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-ellison-oracle-wealth-tesla-stock-billionaires-rich-list-ai-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20world's%20fourth%20richest%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founded%20The%20Ellison%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20as%20a%20research%20and%20development%20center%20for%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20center%20announced%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20campus%20in%20Oxford%20in%202023%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20open%20in%202027.%20The%20%241.27%20billion%20development%20will%20include%20labs%2C%20supercomputing%20facilities%2C%20and%20cancer%20research%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EIT%20will%20inject%20millions%20into%20joint%20research%20projects%20with%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%20to%20dedicate%20to%20what%20Professor%20Irene%20Tracey%2C%20the%20university's%20vice-chancellor%2C%20described%20in%20a%20press%20release%20as%20%26quot%3Bhumanity's%20most%20pressing%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20center's%20research%20will%20focus%20on%20EIT's%20four%20%26quot%3BHumane%20Endeavours%26quot%3B%3A%20health%20and%20medical%20science%2C%20sustainable%20agriculture%2C%20clean%20energy%2C%20and%20government%20innovation%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Sir%20John%20Bell%2C%20the%20president%20of%20EIT%20Oxford%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20alliance%20%26quot%3Bcomes%20at%20an%20exciting%20time%20in%20the%20technological%20revolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20combining%20world-class%20research%20with%20long-term%20capital%20investment%20and%20state-of-the-art%20facilities%2C%20we%20will%20tackle%20some%20of%20society's%20biggest%20challenge