ief%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20to%20board%20the%20pronatalist%20bandwagon.%20Speaking%20at%20a%20Nagpur%20clan%20gathering%2C%20Bhagwat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fcouples-should-have-at-least-3-children-rss-chief-mohan-bhagwat-101733114550752.html%5C%22%3Eexhorted%3C%2Fa%3E%20couples%20to%20have%20three%20children%20each.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India's%20population%20fertility%20rate%20is%20falling%20precariously.%20%E2%80%9CModern%20demographic%20studies%20indicate%20that%20when%20the%20population%20of%20a%20community%20falls%20below%20a%20fertility%20rate%20of%202.1%2C%20that%20society%20faces%20extinction.%20It%20does%20not%20need%20external%20threats%20to%20vanish%3B%20it%20disappears%20on%20its%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagwat%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20population%20replacement%20rate%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20between%202.1%20and%202.3.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20chief%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20urging%20couples%20to%20show%20up%20for%20national%20service.%20Attending%20a%20mass%20wedding%20in%20October%2C%20where%2031%20couples%20tied%20the%20knot%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fmk-stalin-joins-chandrababu-naidu-in-promoting-larger-families-asks-tamil-nadu-couples-to-raise-16-kids-heres-why-11729517624672.html%5C%22%3Espun%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20old%20Tamil%20blessing%20of%20prosperity%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9816'%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStalin%20And%20Naidu%20Bat%20For%20More%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStalin%20sees%20having%20children%20as%20a%20political%20act%20in%20service%20of%20the%20state.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20southern%20states%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20have%20successfully%20controlled%20their%20population%20growth%20rates.%20It%20has%20helped%20them%20improve%20per%20capita%20incomes%20and%20state%20capacity%20to%20deliver%20services%20to%20their%20citizens.%20The%20population%20decline%2C%20however%2C%20affected%20their%20share%20of%20the%20national%20resources%20pie.%20The%20headcount%20of%20a%20state%20and%20its%20economic%20condition%20have%20the%20most%20weightage%20when%20the%20Finance%20Commission%20determines%20the%20formula%20for%20dividing%20central%20tax%20collections.%20That%20means%20states%20that%20controlled%20their%20population%20growth%20are%20seemingly%20punished%20for%20their%20efficiency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20going%20one%20step%20ahead%20and%20planning%20to%20incentivise%20those%20who%20produce%20more%20children%20and%20rap%20those%20who%20have%20less.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20repealed%20the%20earlier%20law%20barring%20people%20with%20more%20than%20two%20children%20from%20contesting%20local%20body%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fhyderabad%2Fchandrababu-naidu-legislation-young-population-andhra-pradesh-9629750%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20bring%20in%20a%20new%20law%20to%20make%20only%20those%20with%20more%20than%20two%20children%20eligible%20to%20contest.''%20Naidu%20worries%20that%20Andhra%20will%20mirror%20Japan%2C%20China%20or%20Europe%E2%80%94more%20old%20people%20than%20young%E2%80%94by%202047.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Population%20Is%20Not%20An%20Advantage%20Anymore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20human%20history%2C%20having%20a%20large%20cohort%20of%20young%20people%20was%20considered%20a%20strength%20as%20it%20meant%20more%20able%20hands%20to%20work%20and%20fight.%20Since%20much%20of%20human%20preoccupation%20during%20most%20of%20that%20history%20has%20centred%20around%20feeding%20and%20procreating%2C%20when%20English%20cleric-economist%20Robert%20Malthus%20made%20a%20dire%20theoretical%20connection%20in%20the%20late%2018th%20century%20between%20demand%2C%20supply%20and%20babies%20born%2C%20it%20shook%20the%20academic%20firmament.%20But%20Malthus%20did%20not%20foresee%20the%20fall%20in%20fertility%20rates.%20He%20also%20failed%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20power%20of%20innovation%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20technological%20progress%20on%20productivity%2C%20potentially%20weakening%20his%20central%20argument%20that%20population%20growth%20will%20ensure%20that%20demand%20would%20far%20outstrip%20supply%20and%20consequently%20impoverishment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20still%20widespread%20poverty%20but%20not%20because%20of%20an%20increase%20in%20population.%20India%20and%20China%20have%20always%20been%20the%20most%20populous%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20Yet%2C%20they%20were%20arguably%20more%20poor%20a%20few%20centuries%20ago%20than%20today%2C%20when%20they%20are%20bursting%20at%20the%20seams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20requirement%20of%20humans%20to%20carry%20out%20tasks%20is%20perhaps%20the%20lowest%20in%20history%20and%20is%20rapidly%20falling%20as%20technological%20advance%20replaces%20humans%20with%20robots.%20Even%20advanced%20thinking%2C%20once%20considered%20the%20sole%20preserve%20of%20humans%2C%20is%20being%20threatened%20by%20artificial%20intelligence.%20Even%20those%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20technological%20progress%2C%20however%2C%20are%20ardent%20pronatalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20chief%20and%20SpaceX%20founder%20Elon%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2024%2F10%2F22%2Felon-musk-people-should-have-kids-ignore-costs%2F%5C%22%3Ebelieves%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20declining%20birth%20rates%20is%20a%20civilizational%20concern.%20Musk%2C%20who%20himself%20has%20fathered%20a%20dozen%20children%2C%20says%20couples%20in%20developed%20countries%20should%20have%20at%20least%20three%20children.%20Don't%20worry%20about%20how%20they%20will%20feed%20and%20live%2C%20he%20suggests%20with%20no%20viable%20plan%20to%20offer.%20Government%20support%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20his%20choice%20as%20he%20has%20been%20entrusted%20by%20US%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20reduce%20government%20spending%2C%20including%20by%20eliminating%20as%20many%20humans%20from%20government%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Really%20Vexes%20RSS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20home%2C%20what's%20vexing%20the%20RSS%20chief%20is%20quite%20something%20else.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbhagwat-reiterates-rss-concern-at-rising-muslim-share-in-population%2Farticleshow%2F87051323.cms%5C%22%3Econcern%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20rising%20share%20of%20the%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20population.%20At%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Pratinidhi%20Sabha%20or%20general%20body%20meeting%20in%202015%2C%20the%20RSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rss.org%2F%2FEncyc%2F2015%2F10%2F31%2Frss-resolution-census-2011-eng.html%5C%22%3Eadopted%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20resolution%20seeking%20strict%20implementation%20of%20population%20control%20policies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20share%20of%20population%20of%20religions%20of%20Bharatiya%20origin%2C%20which%20was%2088%25%2C%20has%20come%20down%20to%2083.8%25%2C%20while%20the%20Muslim%20population%2C%20which%20was%209.8%25%2C%20has%20increased%20to%2014.23%25%20during%20the%20period%201951-2011.%E2%80%9D%20It%20does%20not%20appreciate%2C%20however%2C%20that%20during%20the%20inter-census%20period%20of%202001-2011%2C%20the%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%20was%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20Bihar's%20overall%20population%20growth%20rate.%20It%20also%20does%20not%20acknowledge%20that%20fertility%20rates%20across%20socio-religious%20cohorts%20in%20India%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiaforum.in%2Fsociety%2Frapid-convergence-fertility-across-all-socio-religious-groups-india%5C%22%3Econverge%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Creformulation%20of%20the%20national%20population%20policy%20keeping%20in%20mind%20resource%20availability%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20people%20of%20religions%20of%20Bharatiya%20origin%20were%2099.21%25%20in%201951.%20It%20came%20down%20to%2081.3%25%20in%202001%20and%20to%2067%25%20in%202011.%20In%20just%20one%20decade%2C%20the%20Christian%20population%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20has%20grown%20by%20almost%2013%20percentage%20points.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20the%20population%20of%20Manipur%2C%20the%20share%20of%20religions%20of%20Bharatiya%20origin%2C%20which%20was%20more%20than%2080%25%20in%201951%2C%20has%20come%20down%20to%2050%25%20in%202011.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Tricky%20Question%20For%20RSS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20RSS%2C%20whose%20%3Cem%3Epracharaks%20%3C%2Fem%3Eironically%20have%20to%20remain%20celibate%20as%20long%20as%20they%20are%20in%20the%20organisation%2C%20the%20tribulation%20is%20not%20new.%20It%20started%20after%20the%202001%20socio-economic%20census%20which%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20counted%20Indians%20according%20to%20their%20religion.%20It%20showed%20that%20Muslim%20population%20had%20grown%20at%2036%25%20in%20the%20previous%20decade%2C%20faster%20than%20Hindus%20who%20grew%20at%2020.4%25%20and%20Christians%20at%2022.6%25.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20published%20a%20booklet%20soon%20after%20the%20census%20data%20was%20out%2C%20lamenting%2C%20%26quot%3BHistory%20is%20witness%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20whenever%20majority%20has%20been%20pushed%20to%20a%20position%20of%20minority%2C%20that%20country%20had%20to%20face%20the%20curse%20of%20partition.%26quot%3B%20Sangh%20Parivar%20ideologue%20S.%20Gurumurthy%20commented%20in%20the%20same%20booklet%20that%20%E2%80%9Csecularism%20cannot%20survive%20without%20a%20dominant%20Hindu%20majority%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20does%20Bhagwat's%20Sunday%20statement%20seem%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20RSS%20has%20not-so-subtly%20shifted%20its%20stance%20from%20controlling%20the%20population%20of%20non-Hindus%20to%20increasing%20the%20population%20of%20Hindus%3F%20The%20trigger%20is%20likely%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftwo-more-iskcon-priests-arrested-in-bangladesh-following-chinmoy-krishna-dass-detention%2Farticleshow%2F115848147.cms%5C%22%3Earrest%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Hindu%20priests%20and%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20origin%20of%20the%20trepidation%20is%20in%20an%20RSS%20seminar%20held%20in%202003%2C%20where%20researchers%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Studies%20presented%20from%20their%20study%20%3Cem%3EReligious%20Demography%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20presenter%2C%20JK%20Bajaj%2C%20said%20data%20showed%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20could%20become%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20Indian%20region%E2%80%94encompassing%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%E2%80%94early%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%2021st%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraging%20procreation%20in%20male-dominated%2C%20overcrowded%20societies%20tends%20to%20ignore%20the%20wishes%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20half%20of%20the%20population%20that%20actually%20bears%20children.%20In%20India%2C%20where%20women%20are%20vanishing%20from%20the%20workforce%2C%20upward%20professional%20mobility%20is%20restricted%2C%20and%20social%20obligations%20are%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fmithali-raj-reveals-suitor-told-her-to-let-go-cricket-after-marriage-shaadi-ke-baad-toh-bachhe-dekhne-padenge-na-101733200937208.html%5C%22%3Eoppressive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alluding%20to%20bearing%20children%20as%20a%20national%20duty%20is%20grossly%20unfair.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20begs%20another%20question%3A%20Does%20the%20flip%20to%20pronatalism%20also