ach%20electoral%20verdict!%20The%20voters%20of%20India%20truly%20delivered%20a%20diversity%20dividend%20in%20the%20elections.%20The%20year%20began%20with%20the%20BJP%20feeling%20upbeat%20after%20securing%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20victories%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20by%20the%20end%20of%202023.%20Confident%20(some%20might%20say%20over-confident)%20of%20maintaining%20this%20momentum%2C%20they%20moved%20forward%20with%20optimism.%20However%2C%20the%20year%20ended%20on%20a%20more%20sombre%20note%2C%20with%20the%20NDA%20alliance%20notching%20some%20important%20victories%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20found%20solace%20in%20retaining%20Jharkhand%20but%20lost%20momentum%20in%20other%20electoral%20contests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%2C%20with%20an%20energetic%20campaign%20launched%20by%20all%20key%20players.%20The%20BJP-led%20NDA%20was%20aiming%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20with%20an%20enhanced%20majority%20for%20the%20BJP%20on%20its%20own.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Congress%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20stitching%20together%20a%20fragile%20INDIA%20coalition%2C%20which%20faced%20numerous%20setbacks%2C%20critical%20desertions%2C%20and%20many%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20electoral%20game%20plan%20was%20carefully%20crafted.%20They%20positioned%20themselves%20as%20the%20key%20player%20within%20the%20NDA%20coalition%2C%20setting%20a%20tactical%20target%20of%20370%20plus%20seats%20for%20themselves%20and%20400%2B%20for%20the%20alliance.%20These%20targets%20reflected%20the%20changing%20power%20dynamics%20within%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2019%20vs%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP's%20partners%20in%20the%20NDA%20had%20won%2050%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20(and%20the%20NDA)%20heavily%20relied%20on%20the%20charisma%20and%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20central%20to%20their%20campaign.%20The%20370%2B%20slogan%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20400%2B%20target%20for%20the%20NDA%20were%20attempts%20to%20build%20a%20perception%20of%20invincibility.%20The%20number%20370%20also%20evoked%20memories%20of%20one%20of%20their%20first%20major%20actions%20after%20the%202019%20elections%E2%80%94the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%20Going%20beyond%20400%20was%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20setting%20a%20record%2C%20surpassing%20the%201984%20performance%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi-led%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20a%20key%20player%20but%20not%20the%20dominant%20force.%20After%20setbacks%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20party%20found%20itself%20on%20the%20back%20foot%2C%20with%20few%20bargaining%20chips%20in%20discussions%20with%20its%20allies.%20The%20coalition%20itself%20experienced%20several%20reversals%2C%20with%20the%20JD(U)%20moving%20to%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20playing%20a%20game%20of%20selective%20engagement%20and%20disengagement.%20There%20was%20very%20little%20joint%20campaign%20effort%20or%20common%20strategy%3B%20opposing%20the%20BJP%20was%20the%20only%20glue%20that%20held%20them%20together.%20They%20failed%20to%20reach%20an%20understanding%20in%20key%20states%20like%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%2C%20where%20they%20contested%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Discerning%20Indian%20Voter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20served%20as%20further%20proof%20of%20the%20Indian%20voter's%20innate%20wisdom%20and%20sagacity.%20After%20a%20decade%2C%20we%20were%20back%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20no%20party%20achieved%20a%20clear%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20INDIA%20coalition%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20its%20numbers%2C%20and%20once%20again%2C%20after%20a%20decade%2C%20we%20had%20an%20official%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Congress%2C%20with%20its%20leader%20being%20appointed%20as%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20The%20BJP's%20decline%20from%20303%20to%20240%20seats%20was%20largely%20due%20to%20losses%20in%20five%20states%E2%80%94Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Maharashtra.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20alone%20accounted%20for%20a%20loss%20of%2029%20seats%2C%20which%20made%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20majority%20mark%20and%20the%20final%20seat%20count.%20However%2C%20a%20further%20decline%20below%20240%20was%20prevented%20by%20strong%20performances%20in%20Odisha%2C%20Telangana%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20verdict%20is%20often%20viewed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdiversity%20dividend%E2%80%9D%20offered%20by%20the%20voter.%20Within%20a%20region%2C%20the%20results%20on%20different%20states%20were%20distinctly%20different.%20The%20five%20states%20of%20South%20India%2C%20each%20gave%20a%20different%20verdict.%20This%20underscores%20the%20fact%20that%20states%20have%20become%20the%20centre%20of%20Indian%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20Battles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20was%20carried%20forward%20into%20the%20Assembly%20elections.%20The%20Congress's%20overconfidence%20cost%20them%20a%20victory%20that%20seemed%20clearly%20within%20their%20grasp%20in%20Haryana.%20An%20overemphasis%20on%20consolidating%20the%20Jat%20vote%20backfired%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20countervailing%20non-Jat%20consolidation%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20on%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20a%20limited%20Jat%20coalition%20in%20favour%20of%20Congress%20on%20the%20other.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20internal%20infighting%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20benefitted%20from%20a%20quiet%2C%20ground-level%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%2C%20in%20alliance%20with%20Congress%2C%20won%20the%20elections.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20a%20clear%20divide%20between%20the%20Jammu%20region%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley.%20The%20BJP%20performed%20well%20in%20Jammu%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20struggled%20to%20assert%20its%20presence%20there.%20The%20National%20Conference%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20fared%20better%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley.%20Once%20the%20new%20National%20Conference%20government%20was%20formed%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20attempted%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Centre%20to%20advance%20the%20demand%20for%20statehood%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20There%20also%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20unease%20(or%20unease%3F)%20in%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20Congress%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20choosing%20not%20to%20join%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurtain%20Down%20With%20Maharashtra%20And%20Jharkhand%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20ended%20with%20the%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20elections.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20swept%20to%20power%2C%20while%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20was%20decisively%20defeated.%20All%20three%20partners%20of%20the%20Aghadi%E2%80%94the%20Congress%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%E2%80%94performed%20poorly%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20landslide%20majority%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20alliance.%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20battle%20was%20primarily%20between%20the%20support%20bases%20in%20the%20tribal%20and%20non-tribal%20belts.%20The%20INDIA%20coalition%20did%20well%20by%20consolidating%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20and%20expanding%20its%20reach%20in%20the%20non-tribal%20areas.%20The%20JMM%20alliance%20with%20Congress%2C%20RJD%2C%20and%20Communist%20parties%20contributed%20to%20this%20success.%20The%20BJP%20maintained%20a%20stronghold%20in%20non-tribal%20areas%20but%20failed%20to%20significantly%20dent%20the%20JMM's%20support%20in%20tribal%20areas.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20JMM-led%20government%20worked%20in%20their%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20it%20was%20a%20year%20marked%20by%20many%20unexpected%20shifts%20and%20unanticipated%20turns.%20Each%20electoral%20outcome%20was%20shaped%20by%20a%20unique%20set%20of%20contextual%20factors%2C%20including%20critical%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20specificities.%20The%20multiverse%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20was%20truly%20on%20display%20in%20the%20year%20we%20are%20soon%20bidding%20farewell%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr.%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20is%20the%20National%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20Lokniti%20Network)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733224140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flfnrj0b_voting_625x300_20_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-in-2024-a-reflection-of-indias-diversity-dividend-7162590%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20in%20all%2C%20it%20was%20a%20year%20marked%20by%20many%20unexpected%20shifts%20and%20unanticipated%20turns.%20Each%20electoral%20outcome%20was%20shaped%20by%20a%20unique%20set%20of%20contextual%20factors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-in-2024-a-reflection-of-indias-diversity-dividend-7162590%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20was%20an%20expat%20working%20in%20Dubai%20for%204%20years.%20The%20culture%20of%20splurging%20on%20luxuries%20made%20saving%20harder%20than%20I%20expected.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Victoria%20Blinova%20on%20a%20yacht.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%