flatmate%3F%26quot%3B%20They%20weren't%20bullying%20me%2C%20but%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20drove%20a%20used%20Nissan%20Juke%2C%20which%20is%20a%20nice%20car%20in%20London.%20But%20in%20Dubai%2C%20people%20would%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20not%20driving%20an%20Audi%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20response%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%2025.%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20buy%20a%20Mercedes%20or%20an%20Audi%2C%20especially%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20buy%20it%20new.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20car%20in%20Dubai.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6746dc289f2901eb603735aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221674%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERenting%20a%20used%20car%20or%20having%20a%20roommate%20weren't%20normal%20money-saving%20tricks%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Blinova%20said.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Victoria%20Blinova%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20club%2C%20and%20if%20I%20did%2C%20it%20was%20very%20rarely.%20Clubbing%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20in%20Dubai%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20people%20spend%20a%20lot%20on%20it.%20I%20also%20didn't%20spend%20money%20on%20luxurious%20brands%2C%20clothes%2C%20or%20handbags%2C%20because%20I%20didn't%20really%20care%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emindset%20is%20that%20if%20I%20have%20money%20to%20spend%2C%20that%20means%20I%20have%20money%20to%20save.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I'd%20say%2080%20to%2090%25%20of%20my%20surrounding%20peers%2C%20even%20the%20smartest%20people%20I%20knew%2C%20would%20literally%20live%20paycheck%20to%20paycheck.%20People%20opt%20into%20luxury%20automatically%20because%20it's%20relatively%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20becomes%20part%20of%20your%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20this%20is%20when%20you%20spend%20all%20your%20money.%20I%20found%20it%20an%20ongoing%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20family%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20ea