on%20Commissioner%20and%20Election%20Commissioners.%20The%20matter%20was%20sent%20to%20another%20bench%20and%20hearings%20will%20begin%20January%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Khanna%20-%20then%20a%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20was%20part%20of%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20that%20began%20hearing%20those%20petitions%20in%20March%20and%20subsequently%20passed%20an%20interim%20order.%20Now%2C%20however%2C%20Mr%20Khanna%20said%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20scenario%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-sanjiv-khanna-sworn-in-as-51st-chief-justice-of-india-6990958%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappointment%20as%20Chief%20Justice%20last%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20in%20a%20judgement%20meant%20to%20insulate%20the%20Election%20Commission%20from%20interference%20by%20the%20Legislature%20-%20said%20Chief%20Election%20and%20Election%20Commissioners%20would%20be%20appointed%20by%20a%20three-member%20panel%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20months%20later%20the%20government%20introduced%20and%20passed%20-%20in%20a%20Winter%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20even%20as%20most%20of%20the%20opposition%20was%20suspended%20-%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20other%20Election%20Commissioners%20Bill%2C%20which%20dropped%20the%20CJI%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20union%20minister%20to%20be%20named%20by%20the%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbill-to-appoint-top-3-election-commissioners-passed-in-lok-sabha-4715210%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20To%20Appoint%20Top%203%20Poll%20Officers%20Passed%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Clears%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20was%20challenged%20-%20days%20before