Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink%20To%20Hunt%20Down%20Drugs%20Smugglers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20police%20will%20seek%20details%20from%20Elon%20Musk's%20Starlink%2C%20they%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20hunt%20down%20drug%20smugglers%20who%20used%20its%20satellite%20internet%20device%20to%20navigate%20deep%20seas%20and%20bring%20meth%20worth%20%244.25%20billion%20into%20Indian%20waters%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20biggest%20such%20seizure%2C%20police%20in%20the%20remote%20outpost%20of%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20islands%20uncovered%20more%20than%206%2C000%20kg%20(13%2C000%20lb)%20of%20meth%20last%20week%20in%20a%20Myanmar%20boat%20carying%20sacks%20of%20suspected%20contraband%2C%20and%20detained%20six%20Myanmar%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20incident%20has%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells%20as%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20Starlink's%20device%20has%20been%20used%20to%20navigate%20and%20reach%20Indian%20waters%2C%20Hargobinder%20S.%20Dhaliwal%2C%20a%20top%20police%20officer%20in%20the%20Andaman%20islands%20who%20is%20handling%20the%20case%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%2C%20which%20says%20it%20provides%20coverage%20in%20international%20waters%2C%20has%20plans%20to%20launch%20in%20India%2C%20but%20says%20its%20coverage%20in%20territorial%20waters%20is%20contingent%20on%20government%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20(case)%20is%20different%20because%20it%20is%20bypassing%20all%20the%20legal%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhaliwal%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20directly%20operated%20(phones)%20with%20satellite%2C%20creating%20a%20Wi-Fi%20hotspot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20planned%20to%20seek%20from%20Starlink%20details%20such%20as%20who%20bought%20the%20device%20and%20when%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20usage%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(smugglers)%20were%20using%20Starlink%20since%20their%20journey%20started%20from%20Myanmar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndaman%20and%20Nicobar%20police%20estimated%20the%20seized%20meth%20had%20a%20retail%20market%20value%20of%20360%20billion%20rupees%20(%244.25%20billion).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20inquiry%20comes%20as%20Starlink%20inches%20closer%20to%20a%20launch%20in%20India%20after%20lobbying%20for%20months%20to%20secure%20satellite%20spectrum%2C%20following%20a%20face-off%20with%20Indian%20billionaire%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20who%20repeatedly%20opposed%20the%20move%20and%20urged%20spectrum%20auctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhaliwal%20said%20the%20smugglers%20used%20the%20Starlink%20Mini%20device%2C%20described%20on%20its%20website%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20compact%2C%20portable%20kit%20that%20can%20easily%20fit%20in%20a%20backpack%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20islands%20have%20said%20they%20are%20checking%20the%20involvement%20of%20any%20local%20or%20foreign%20syndicates%20in%20the%20whole%20network%20as%20they%20tackle%20the%20latest%20seizure%20case%20from%20various%20angles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20seizures%20of%20methamphetamine%2C%20or%20meth%2C%20as%20it%20is%20known%2C%20reached%20a%20record%20high%20of%20190%20tons%20in%20east%20and%20southeast%20Asia%2C%20as%20meth%20trafficking%20on%20maritime%20routes%20has%20increased%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20on%20Drugs%20and%20Crime%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20growing%20transit%20and%20destination%20market%20for%20methamphetamine%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20UNODC%20said%20in%20its%20report%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733218380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnl7d