Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20has%20the%20capability%20of%20leading%20the%20team%20and%20he's%20a%20team's%20man.%20You%20look%20at%20him%20he%20never%20only%20talks%20about%20himself%2C%20he%20talks%20about%20the%20team%2C%20the%20other%20players.%20What%20advice%20he%20would%20give%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20captained%20India%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20regular%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20led%20the%20team%20to%20a%20commanding%20victory%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20Australia%2C%20silencing%20critics%20and%20proving%20his%20mettle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20tour%20of%20Australia%20began%20under%20challenging%20circumstances%2C%20with%20the%20team%20reeling%20from%20a%20disappointing%200-3%20home%20series%20loss%20to%20New%20Zealand.%20That%20loss%20not%20only%20hurt%20morale%20but%20also%20severely%20dented%20India's%20chances%20of%20reaching%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bumrah%20rose%20to%20the%20occasion%2C%20delivering%20a%20spellbinding%20opening%20spell%20that%20dismantled%20the%20Australian%20batting%20lineup%20on%20their%20home%20soil.%20His%20performance%20was%20pivotal%20in%20setting%20the%20tone%20for%20a%20dominant%20Indian%20victory%2C%20showcasing%20both%20his%20skill%20as%20a%20bowler%20and%20his%20ability%20to%20inspire%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPujara%20emphasised%20Bumrah's%20qualities%20that%20make%20him%20an%20excellent%20leader.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20the%20capability%20of%20leading%20the%20team%2C%20and%20he's%20a%20team%20man.%20He%20never%20talks%20about%20himself%20alone%3B%20he%20always%20puts%20the%20team%20and%20other%20players%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Pujara%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Bumrah's%20standout%20traits%2C%20according%20to%20Pujara%2C%20is%20his%20humility%20and%20ability%20to%20adapt%20to%20situations.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20times%20when%20players%20don't%20need%20advice%2C%20and%20he%20accepts%20that.%20If%20there's%20an%20experienced%20player%20in%20the%20team%2C%20he%20keeps%20quiet.%20That's%20the%20sign%20of%20a%20good%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPujara%20also%20highlighted%20Bumrah's%20approachable%20demeanour%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20very%20down-to-earth%2C%20friendly%20with%20players%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20and%20always%20eager%20to%20help.%20Even%20outside%20cricket%2C%20he%20has%20a%20humble%20personality%20and%20is%20a%20great%20person%20to%20chat%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20will%20hand%20the%20captaincy%20reins%20back%20to%20Rohit%20Sharma%20for%20the%20second%20Test%2C%20a%20pink-ball%20match%20in%20Adelaide%20starting%20December%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733214960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F24hd3ivg_ssc_625x300_02_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fon-jasprit-bumrah-as-indias-long-term-captaincy-option-cheteshwar-pujaras-capability-verdict-7154766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20has%20endorsed%20pace-ace%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20as%20a%20viable%20long-term%20captaincy%20candidate%20for%20India%2C%20once%20Rohit%20Sharma%20steps%20down.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fon-jasprit-bumrah-as-indias-long-term-captaincy-option-cheteshwar-pujaras-capability-verdict-7154766%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Avoid%20Saffron%20Robes%2C%20Tilak%20In%20Public'%3A%20ISKCON%20Monk's%20Bangladesh%20Advisory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EISKCON%20Kolkata%20spokesperson%20Radharamn%20Das%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20he%20has%20urged%20its%20monks%20and%20followers%20from%20Bangladesh%20to%20avoid%20wearing%20saffron%20robes%20and%20'tilak'%20in%20public%2C%20advising%20them%20to%20practice%20their%20faith%20discreetl