the%20satisfaction%20of%20drinking%20milk%20from%20my%20own%20cow%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20named%20Rivan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20urban%20cities%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20or%20space%20to%20care%20for%20the%20cow.%20This%20model%20fulfils%20that%20in%20the%20best%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Puspanjali%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%2C%20who%20has%20Celiac%20disease%2C%20highlights%20the%20product%E2%80%99s%20health%20benefits.%20%E2%80%9CPackaged%20milk%20always%20causes%20allergic%20reactions%20for%20me.%20But%20for%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20no%20issues%20with%20their%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Graphic%20explanation%20of%20Cow%20Currency%20and%20its%20benefits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283-294x300.jpg%20294w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283-500x510.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-11_11zon-1732802283-150x153.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384022%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22632%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGraphic%20explanation%20of%20Cow%20Currency%20and%20its%20benefits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EEthical%20treatment%20of%20cows%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Cow%20Currency%E2%80%99s%20phi