C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jagdish%20Pooniya%2C%2032%2C%20an%20audit%20inspector%20from%20the%20Dhava%20Doli%20Wildlife%20area%2C%20and%20one%20of%20Sharvan%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20key%20collaborators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHands-on%20approach%20to%20wildlife%20conservation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vital%20aspect%20of%20Sharvan%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20been%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20forest%20department%20and%20local%20government%20officials.%20As%20someone%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20department%20for%20over%20five%20years%2C%20he%20has%20seen%20firsthand%20the%20challenges%20they%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20only%20one%20small%20room%20with%20one%20staff%20member%2C%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20means%20to%20help%20injured%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20explains.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20often%20step%20in%20to%20provide%20immediate%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sharvan%20tending%20to%20an%20injured%20deer%2F%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3