Sharvan%20manages%20his%20full%20time%20job%20in%20wildlife%20conservation%20and%20farming%2C%20with%20his%20efforts%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CLuckily%2C%20I%20have%20a%20five-day%20work%20week%2C%20so%20during%20the%20weekends%2C%20I%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20work.%20But%20since%20my%20job%20is%20to%20be%20on%20field%20and%20interact%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20even%20that%20helps%20me%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20what%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20in%20terms%20of%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20there%2C%20other%20people%2C%20especially%20my%20friends%2C%20Jagdish%20and%20Radheshyam%2C%20take%20care%20of%20everything.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWildlife%20conservation%20is%20something%20that%20our%20entire%20community%20is%20committed%20to.%20But%20I%20especially%20feel%20for%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Bustard%2C%20which%20has%20been%20declared%20the%20most%20critically%20endangered%20species%20of%20birds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2028-year-old%20Radheshyam%20Bishnoi.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20December%2C%20all%20the%20water%20sources%20usually%20dry%20up%2C%20so%20we%20regularly%20refill%2010%2C000-litre%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352370%2Fsave-birds-in-heatwaves-summer-free-bird-feeders-kapil-prajapat-sirohi-ngo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatering%20holes%20to%20help%20bi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F233508%2Fwater-well-digging-cost-farmers-irrigation-karnataka-professor-digs-open-well-ancestral-village-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erds%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20vultures%2C%20eagles%2C%20and%20bustards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20deal%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20poaching%2C%20Radheshyam%20has%20formed%20a%20community%20of%20people%20in%20poaching-prone%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20t