0every%20screening%2C%20regular%20meetings%20are%20conducted%20where%20people%20can%20voice%20their%20concerns%20and%20share%20suggestions.%20These%20meetings%20tackle%20a%20variety%20of%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20including%20corruption%2C%20abuse%2C%20pension%20issues%2C%20and%20harmful%20superstition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20children%20of%20these%20communities%2C%20who%20would%E2%80%99ve%20otherwise%20gotten%20involved%20in%20other%20activities%2C%20are%20mobilised%20to%20work%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20their%20own%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20the%20marginalised%20into%20mainstream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadiwasi%20Janjagruti%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20have%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20community.%20By%20translating%20government%20policies%20into%20the%20local%20dialect%20and%20using%20video%20formats%20to%20explain%20them%2C%20they%20are%20ensuring%20that%20the%20tribal%20population%20is%20not%20left%20out%20of%20important%20decisions%20that%20affect%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID%2C%20when%20hyperlocal%20information%20became%20crucial%2C%20Nitesh%20and%20his%20team%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20ensure%20the%20community%20stayed%20informed.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20take%20the%20WHO%20reports%2C%20translate%20them%20into%20Hindi%2C%20and%20then%20our%20team%20members%20would%20further%20translate%20them%20into%20our%20local%20dialect%2C%20Pawari.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20content%20was%20available%20in%20Marathi%2C%20we%20already%20had%20the%20information%20ready%20for%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20has%20successfully%20addressed%20several%20local%20issues%2C%20making%20a%20tangible%20difference%20in%20the%20community.%20One%20such%20case%20involved%20a%20woman%20whose%20nine%20goats%20died%20from%20poisoning.%20While%20the%20loss%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20significant%20enough%20by%20mainstream%20news%20outlets%2C